Cosmos University: Plants Databank

This Databank contains entries on five hundred and ninety-five plants and lists their scientific, magical, ritualistic, and metaphysical propetries. This information is currently being gathered and updated as we accumulate it. This directory is scheduled to receive a major interface update shortly.


If you're interested in helping create this databank:
  • Look for any incorrect data
  • Suggest data fields we could add
  • Suggest plants we may have missed
  • Folk names are hard to track down and map correctly, often we create duplicate entries because of an archaic folk name being replaced with a common folk name - be on the look out for records like this
  • We're facing a large backlog of scientific data that must be processed into these records
  • If you'd like to help, please join our Discord and make suggestions in the databanks -> #plants channel
